description:
Go behind the scenes with Heroes 2 project manager, Jefferson Nascimento as he shares how and why an international team decided to create Heroes 2. Jefferson shares whats new and improved about Heroes 2 as well the vision for how the game will continue to grow. Heroes 2 is not just a game. Its a movement of ordinary people called to be superheroes.

Learn more at: https://www.heroesbibletrivia.org/en/
